snippet.title: Plants vs. Zombies Garden Warfare 2013 Zombie Class Reveal
snippet.description:
Plants vs. Zombies: Garden Warfare Zombie Class Reveal

You saw the plants at E3 2013, now the Zombies get their their chance to take it to the streets and gardens! 

Watch the zombies in multiplayer action, Soldier Zombie, Scientist, the Engineer and All-Star as they exploit the latest Zomboss technology to overwhelm and distract plant defenses.
